{
  "page": "Tywald Lannister",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/50px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/75px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/100px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Tywald Lannister</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/50px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/75px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/100px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Tywald_Lannister.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Tywald Lannister.png\" src=\"/images/e/e7/Tywald_Lannister.png\" width=\"269\" height=\"560\" /></a><div>Tywald Lannister as depicted in <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <i>Histories &amp; Lore</i>.</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/211_AC\" title=\"211 AC\">211</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/219_AC\" title=\"219 AC\">219&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Storming_of_Starpike\" title=\"Storming of Starpike\">Starpike</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Lannister\" title=\"Gerold Lannister\">Gerold Lannister</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Tywald Lannister</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>, the eldest son and heir of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Lannister\" title=\"Gerold Lannister\">Gerold Lannister</a> and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>, the twin of <a href=\"/index.php/Tion_Lannister\" title=\"Tion Lannister\">Tion</a> and elder brother of <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Lannister\" title=\"Tytos Lannister\">Tytos</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jason_Lannister_(son_of_Gerold)\" title=\"Jason Lannister (son of Gerold)\">Jason Lannister</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafappendix:_lannister_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafappendix:_lannister_lineage.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tywald_Lannister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Maester <a href=\"/index.php/Yandel\" title=\"Yandel\">Yandel</a> refers to Tywald and Tion as <i>Gerold's glorious twins</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tywald_Lannister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Tywald was the eldest son of <a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Lannister\" title=\"Gerold Lannister\">Gerold the Golden</a>, Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>, and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Rohanne_Webber\" title=\"Rohanne Webber\">Rohanne Webber</a>, his second wife. In his youth, Tywald was betrothed to <a href=\"/index.php/Ellyn_Reyne\" title=\"Ellyn Reyne\">Ellyn Reyne</a> and was a squire to her father, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Reyne\" title=\"Robert Reyne\">Robert Reyne</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Castamere\" title=\"Castamere\">Castamere</a>.\n</p><p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Peake_Uprising\" title=\"Peake Uprising\">Peake Uprising</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233&#160;AC</a>, Tywald fought on the side of King <a href=\"/index.php/Maekar_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maekar I Targaryen\">Maekar I Targaryen</a>, but he was mortally wounded by a spear at <a href=\"/index.php/Storming_of_Starpike\" title=\"Storming of Starpike\">Starpike</a>. Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_V_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon V Targaryen\">Aegon Targaryen</a> knighted the squire, while Tywald laid dying in his twin brother <a href=\"/index.php/Tion_Lannister\" title=\"Tion Lannister\">Tion's</a> arms. According to a semi-canon source, Tywald asked his brother to \"take care of Lady Ellyn\" with his final words. This later led Lord Gerold to agree to a betrothal between Tion and Ellyn.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_westerlands:_house_lannister_under_the_dragons.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Tywald_Lannister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Damon_Lannister_(lord)\" title=\"Damon Lannister (lord)\">Damon</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Cerissa_Brax\" title=\"Cerissa Brax\">Cerissa<br />Brax</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"><td style=\"border-right:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px 